2.26.20  2:01 am   Bill your music almost got me in trouble with the law, but then it fixed it. I'll explain. I was driving up the North West Coastal Highway, it was a long drive, i was listening to my Bill playlist and 'long long long journey' was playing (my absolute favourite) and i had subconsciously picked up speed, which sometimes happens when i listen to a song i really like. Then 'slow down' started and i checked my speed and was like 'o shit i am going 15kms over the limit' so i slowed down. And over the next hill was a police car! Holy moly what a close one. Your music made the drive much nicer, even though it made my accelerator foot a bit over-enthusiastic
